User recreate via the command "make:user" use the make auth to begin the auth creation

Creating a new trick I'm creating a newtricktype and newTrickController It is working Now i must work on an upload system for images and videos

Creating some new type (addImage and addVideo) Creating some new Controller (addImageToTrick and Video) Creating some views for them Now i will work for the upload system and make the functionnality to add images and videos to an existing trick.

Upload system is working fine. User can now upload images directly from their computer. Add videos is now possible too just by copying the iframe given. Add a test on video in order to have just Youtube,Daylimotion or Vimeo supported.
Elements of the tricks can now be updated.
Updating the tricks is now fully working
Rework of video upload done. from now on we only store url in database. User will post an iframe like always but we only keep url in order to create our own iframe.
Users can now create an account. Now i'll try to add a forgotten password functionality.
Forgotten password ? I'm trying to add this
Forgotten password functionality is ready and working good.
